          <span class="text-accent">&gt;</span> I'm a software engineer who builds products, not just features. Over the past 6 years I've gone from writing my first lines of code to shipping revenue-generating applications used by thousands of people daily.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-fg-muted">
